 Abuja – Apostle Johnson Suleman, the founder of the Omega Fire Ministries, has excited his followers with a stunning story he recently told. The pastor, who told his story on Twitter, revealed that he had once fasted for 11 days and began stooling blood afterwards. The clergyman made the revelation in some tweets today Thursday, October 3rd. According to him, he was so hungry for the annointing that he forgot to apply wisdom in what he did. Below is how he told his story. Source